name: Tri-County Health
tweet: As you prepare for Thanksgiving, there is no need to rinse or wash raw turkey. Poultry juices can spread in the kitchen and contaminate other foods, utensils, and countertops. Find safe food handling tips to keep you and your family from getting sick at  https://t.co/kNDZCPzDJE.  https://t.co/A5OcNZXzss
